** Ruby/CVS - CVS library for Ruby **

Ruby/CVS is a library to access a CVS repository.

* Home page

http://cvs.m17n.org/~akr/ruby-cvs/

* Requirements

  ruby-1.7.1	(older version may work.)
  http://www.ruby-lang.org/ 

  cvs-1.11.1p1	(older version may work.)
  http://www.cvshome.org/

  rcs-5.7	(older version may work.)
  ftp://ftp.cs.purdue.edu/pub/RCS/

  flex.rb-0.10	(optional.  older version doesn't work.)
  http://www.inf.bme.hu/~pts/flex_rb-latest.tar.gz
  (it makes parsing rcs file faster.)

* Samples

  ReViz: ViewCVS like CGI script.  See reviz/*.
  VizTree: Branch Tree Visualizer.  See viztree.

* Author

Tanaka Akira <akr@m17n.org>
http://cvs.m17n.org/~akr/
